snippet.title: Nitrome - Sky Serpents Any% Speedrun PB 9:05
snippet.description:
sub for more content! expand the description for a short analysis!
more details about the run on speedrun.com/sky_serpents





Holy smokes, what a run. On level 13, I got gassed, which essentially minimizes my walk to a crawl and my jump to nearly no height. Somehow, in the next two levels, I gathered enough time save to PB yet again by *literally* a second.

As such, this run was too messy in my opinion. My PB of 9:07 before demonstrates much cleaner tech and strat performance, but I suppose the idea of PB'ing again for this run in particular just gave me that mental edge to pull through. And that I did.
